WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.467 --> 00:00:04.968
♪♪

00:00:04.968 --> 00:00:07.334
Narrator:
WHEN PROFESSIONAL BOXERS
WIN A TITLE,

00:00:07.334 --> 00:00:08.601
THEY'RE CROWNED THE CHAMP

00:00:08.601 --> 00:00:11.667
AND REWARDED WITH A BELT
TO BE WORN AROUND THE WAIST.

00:00:11.667 --> 00:00:14.767
EACH INTERNATIONAL ORGANIZATION
COMMISSIONS A BELT

00:00:14.767 --> 00:00:17.601
THAT'S CUSTOM-DESIGNED
TO ITS SPECIFICATIONS

00:00:17.601 --> 00:00:20.634
AND PROMINENTLY FEATURES
THE ORGANIZATION'S LOGO

00:00:20.634 --> 00:00:23.834
IN THE BELT'S CENTRAL MEDALLION.

00:00:23.834 --> 00:00:26.567
[ TRANQUIL HIP HOP PLAYS ]
THESE BOXING CHAMPIONSHIP BELTS

00:00:26.567 --> 00:00:28.767
ARE ENTIRELY HANDCRAFTED.

00:00:28.767 --> 00:00:32.801
THE LATERALS, THE SIDE PIECES
FLANKING THE ORNATE CENTERPLATE,

00:00:32.801 --> 00:00:37.000
ARE SOMETIMES ENGRAVED
WITH THE FIGHTER'S PORTRAIT.

00:00:37.000 --> 00:00:40.334
WHEN A BOXING ASSOCIATION
COMMISSIONS A NEW DESIGN,

00:00:40.334 --> 00:00:44.901
THE COMPANY'S ARTISANS PREPARE
A SKETCH FOR EACH PIECE.

00:00:44.901 --> 00:00:48.667
FOLLOWING THE SKETCH,
THEY SCULPT A CLAY MODEL.

00:00:48.667 --> 00:00:51.834
FROM THAT,
THEY CAST A PLASTER MODEL;

00:00:51.834 --> 00:00:53.834
THEN, A METAL MODEL,

00:00:53.834 --> 00:00:57.267
REFINING THE SCULPTURE
AT EACH STEP.

00:00:57.267 --> 00:00:59.601
ARTISANS USE
THE FINAL METAL MODEL

00:00:59.601 --> 00:01:01.434
TO PRODUCE A RUBBER MOLD,

00:01:01.434 --> 00:01:04.567
WHICH IS USED TO CAST
THE PIECE IN WHITE METAL.

00:01:04.567 --> 00:01:06.634
♪♪

00:01:06.634 --> 00:01:09.234
THE EXTRACTED CASTINGS
ARE QUITE ROUGH,

00:01:09.234 --> 00:01:13.200
SO THE WORKSHOP'S CRAFTSMEN
USE FILES, CHISELS,

00:01:13.200 --> 00:01:15.901
AND AUTOMATED TOOLS
TO REFINE THE SHAPE.

00:01:15.901 --> 00:01:18.334
♪♪

00:01:18.334 --> 00:01:20.100
SOME OF THE DEVICES
AND TECHNIQUES

00:01:20.100 --> 00:01:22.801
ARE ROUTINELY USED BY JEWELERS,

00:01:22.801 --> 00:01:26.067
WHILE OTHERS WERE DESIGNED
SPECIFICALLY FOR THIS PURPOSE.

00:01:26.067 --> 00:01:35.567
♪♪

00:01:35.567 --> 00:01:38.234
ONCE THE INTRICATE DETAILS
ARE COMPLETED,

00:01:38.234 --> 00:01:41.501
THE TEAM FILES DOWN ROUGH SPOTS
ALONG THE PERIMETER.

00:01:41.501 --> 00:01:46.501
♪♪

00:01:46.501 --> 00:01:47.767
THE BELTS FEATURE

00:01:47.767 --> 00:01:50.100
A THREE-DIMENSIONAL
SCULPTURE OF AN EAGLE

00:01:50.100 --> 00:01:52.067
FUSED TO THE CENTERPLATE.

00:01:52.067 --> 00:01:53.434
♪♪

00:01:53.434 --> 00:01:56.300
AN ARTISAN HEATS THE WINGS
WITH AN OPEN FLAME,

00:01:56.300 --> 00:01:57.767
TO MAKE THEM PLIABLE.

00:01:57.767 --> 00:02:00.767
♪♪

00:02:00.767 --> 00:02:04.067
THEN, HE BENDS THEM TO RENDER
THE EAGLE MORE LIFELIKE.

00:02:04.067 --> 00:02:10.701
♪♪

00:02:10.701 --> 00:02:13.434
EVERY PIECE MUST BE
METICULOUSLY HAND-POLISHED

00:02:13.434 --> 00:02:14.868
ON A BUFFING WHEEL.

00:02:14.868 --> 00:02:18.901
THIS PREPARES THE METAL TO BE
PLATED WITH GOLD OR RHODIUM.

00:02:18.901 --> 00:02:25.634
♪♪

00:02:25.634 --> 00:02:29.534
THE PIECE IS ELECTROPLATED
WITH COPPER, THEN NICKEL,

00:02:29.534 --> 00:02:31.667
THEN 18-KARAT GOLD.

00:02:31.667 --> 00:02:38.601
THE NICKEL CARRIES THE SHINE
THROUGH TO THE SURFACE.

00:02:38.601 --> 00:02:41.100
AFTER A THOROUGH BUFFING
ON THE SURFACE,

00:02:41.100 --> 00:02:45.300
THE PIECES ARE EMBELLISHED WITH
CRYSTALS INTO MOLDED CAVITIES.

00:02:45.300 --> 00:02:50.701
♪♪

00:02:50.701 --> 00:02:52.300
SOMETIMES THE
CHAMPIONSHIP WINNER

00:02:52.300 --> 00:02:56.133
MAY ORDER PRECIOUS STONES,
SUCH AS DIAMONDS AND RUBIES,

00:02:56.133 --> 00:02:59.501
TO REPLACE THE CRYSTALS,
DEPENDING ON THEIR PREFERENCE.

00:02:59.501 --> 00:03:02.601
♪♪

00:03:02.601 --> 00:03:05.734
A TEAM OF ENAMELERS
PAINTS THE FINISHED PIECES

00:03:05.734 --> 00:03:08.567
WITH JEWELRY-GRADE ENAMEL.

00:03:08.567 --> 00:03:12.801
THIS REQUIRES A STEADY HAND
AND CLOSE ATTENTION TO DETAIL.

00:03:12.801 --> 00:03:16.601
♪♪

00:03:16.601 --> 00:03:18.267
ONCE THE PIECE IS PAINTED,

00:03:18.267 --> 00:03:20.767
IT'S PUT INTO AN OVEN
TO BAKE THE ENAMEL.

00:03:20.767 --> 00:03:27.033
♪♪

00:03:27.033 --> 00:03:33.000
♪♪

00:03:33.000 --> 00:03:36.334
THE BELT STRAP IS MADE
OF HIGH-GRADE BONDED LEATHER.

00:03:36.334 --> 00:03:39.534
A CRAFTSMAN TRACES A BELT
TEMPLATE IN THE LEATHER,

00:03:39.534 --> 00:03:41.901
THEN CUTS IT OUT WITH A KNIFE.

00:03:41.901 --> 00:03:46.467
THEN, THEY ADHERE THE STRAP
TO LEATHER OR HIGH-GRADE VINYL.

00:03:46.467 --> 00:03:49.400
THE DESIGNER SEWS
THE STRAP'S LINING SEPARATELY,

00:03:49.400 --> 00:03:53.534
STITCHING BLACK SPANDEX
OVER A FAUX-FUR BACKING

00:03:53.534 --> 00:03:55.868
AND ATTACHING
THE AUTHENTICITY LABEL,

00:03:55.868 --> 00:03:58.834
WHICH BEARS
THE BELT'S SERIAL NUMBER.

00:03:58.834 --> 00:04:02.634
THIS DISTINGUISHES IT
FROM CHEAPLY MADE COPIES.

00:04:02.634 --> 00:04:06.000
THE CRAFTSMAN ATTACHES
LEATHER HIGH-GRADE VINYL PIPING

00:04:06.000 --> 00:04:07.834
TO THE STRAP PERIMETER.

00:04:07.834 --> 00:04:09.934
HE PLACES A BRAND STICKER
ON THE BACK,

00:04:09.934 --> 00:04:11.501
NEXT TO AN INSCRIBED TRIBUTE

00:04:11.501 --> 00:04:15.467
TO THE ORIGINATOR
OF THE MODERN BOXING BELT.

00:04:15.467 --> 00:04:17.167
THEY ADHERE THE LINING.

00:04:17.167 --> 00:04:20.634
♪♪

00:04:20.634 --> 00:04:23.033
THEN, AFTER SMOOTHING OUT
THE LAYERS OF THE BELT

00:04:23.033 --> 00:04:24.234
WITH A HAMMER,

00:04:24.234 --> 00:04:27.801
THE DESIGNER STITCHES
THE LINING TO THE STRAP.

00:04:27.801 --> 00:04:32.000
SOME BELTS HAVE BUCKLES;
OTHERS, HOOK-AND-LOOP FASTENERS,

00:04:32.000 --> 00:04:35.334
WHICH ARE STITCHED TO THE STRAP
AT THE SAME TIME AS THE LINING.

00:04:35.334 --> 00:04:39.467
♪♪

00:04:39.467 --> 00:04:41.167
ONCE THE BELT IS FINISHED,

00:04:41.167 --> 00:04:44.167
THE CENTERPLATE AND LATERALS
ARE ATTACHED.

00:04:44.167 --> 00:04:46.968
IT'S ESSENTIAL TO WEAR GLOVES
WHILE DOING THIS,

00:04:46.968 --> 00:04:49.334
TO PROTECT THE PRISTINE SURFACE.

00:04:49.334 --> 00:04:52.467
♪♪

00:04:52.467 --> 00:04:55.801
THE FINAL STEP IS TO PLACE
AN ENGRAVABLE BRASS PLATE

00:04:55.801 --> 00:04:57.334
INTO EACH LATERAL.

00:04:57.334 --> 00:05:00.200
THEN, THE CHAMPIONSHIP BELT
IS DELIVERED

00:05:00.200 --> 00:05:02.934
IN A HAND-CRAFTED,
PROTECTIVE CASE,

00:05:02.934 --> 00:05:05.934
FOR A KNOCKOUT PRESENTATION.

